{
  "stem": "311.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were 700 men, exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we were like this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were aces.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were people who didn't know nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember, I-- I-- and, you know, one of the managers comes in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Listen, you're a smart kid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Can you teach Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Hilstein to-- to work a lathe?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, sure, why not?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hilstein was a philanthropist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was the main man for, you know, for hachsharas, for sending to Israel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Right, he was part of the Zionist--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He must-- I don't know if he, himself, was a rich man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or he was the one-- If you knew Dr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hilstein, first of all, you could go to the camp when you were a little kid, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To a camp, just a Jewish camp from where they help out or there was money from United States.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went once to a camp in Rabka, a winter camp, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So even if you had money, you couldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Still, Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hilstein has to get the OK, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But somehow, my father-- What?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, He was one of the-- he was a philanthropist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this, it was amazing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Hilstein-- what was I, 20--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--21?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A very-- if anything, if any-- he knows.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's amazing how intelligent-- how people, who have knowledge, who-- who have-- I don't know he's a doctor or a dentist or whatever it is-- how fast they pick up to do something.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a small lathe, a precision lathe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I give myself a few hours, myself, you know, to get acquainted with.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a job to do threadings, you know, screws, special screws.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I start doing them.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
